{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"subheading":"<p><strong>{{ page.metafields.custom.sub_title.value }}<\/strong><\/p>","title":"","show_large":false}},"a32aaa6f-5d18-4757-a495-edaa478706ac":{"type":"three-column","blocks":{"template--16109988315305__a32aaa6f-5d18-4757-a495-edaa478706ac-1680042478fd83cee0-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/230628_NatalieMarie_Studio_095_crop.jpg"}}},"block_order":["template--16109988315305__a32aaa6f-5d18-4757-a495-edaa478706ac-1680042478fd83cee0-0"],"settings":{"enable_dark":false,"subheading":"<p><strong>Learn with us<\/strong><\/p>","title":"<p>Education<\/p>","description":"<p>Our business is anchored by shared values that have underpinned our decisions from the brand’s inception, alongside the core belief that we have a responsibility to create as consciously and purposefully as possible. Outlining these intentions in our <strong>Impact Report<\/strong> is our way of inviting you into a world of action, accountability and progress. <\/p><p>We want our community to invest in NMJ because they feel connected; not only to the aesthetic, but to larger story they want their piece to tell. With a focus on combining quality materials that are sourced mindfully, considered design and meticulous production techniques, NMJ pieces are intended to be worn for lifetimes; to become a part of the wearer and to be handed down for generations to come.<\/p><p><\/p><p><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0309\/0645\/files\/NMJ_Strategy_Report_A4_Document_Landscape_2025-31.03_4_MB.pdf?v=1748477328\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0309\/0645\/files\/NMJ_Strategy_Report_A4_Document_Landscape_2025-31.03_4_MB.pdf?v=1748477328\">View Impact Report 2025<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0309\/0645\/files\/NMJ_Impact_Report_2023_and_Beyond.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0309\/0645\/files\/NMJ_Impact_Report_2023_and_Beyond.pdf\">View Impact Report 2023<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0309\/0645\/files\/NMJ_IMPACT_REPORT_2022_and_Beyond_21.07.2022.pdf?v=1658887854\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0309\/0645\/files\/NMJ_IMPACT_REPORT_2022_and_Beyond_21.07.2022.pdf?v=1658887854\">View Impact Report 2022<\/a><\/p>","feature_text":"<p>NMJ pieces are <em>intended to be treasured<\/em>, to become a part of the wearer and to be handed down for <em>generations to come<\/em>.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_metaobject":"","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_metaobject":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_style":"primary"}},"423d7835-8ada-4b96-af05-dd40c80727a4":{"type":"content-list","blocks":{"template--16109988315305__423d7835-8ada-4b96-af05-dd40c80727a4-1680042194a27ec731-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"apply_overlay":false,"devices":"mobile_desktop","content_position":"middleLeft","subheading":"<p><strong>EDUCATION<\/strong><\/p>","title":"<p>Sustainability<\/p>","description":"<p>The intention to create consciously is part of our DNA. As a manufacturer and retailer of fine jewellery, it is of the utmost importance to us to craft responsibly, source mindfully and ensure that all of our pieces are produced sustainably and ethically. From our handmade process and studio practices to our supply chain, learn more about our sustainability journey.<\/p>","description_mobile":"<p>The intention to create consciously is part of our DNA. As a manufacturer and retailer of fine jewellery, it is of the utmost importance to us to craft responsibly, source mindfully and ensure that all of our pieces are produced sustainably and ethically. From our handmade process and studio practices to our supply chain, learn more about our sustainability journey.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_metaobject":"","button_1_text":"Learn More","button_1_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/sustainabil